    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! This car is in truly stunning condition\u2014it\u2019s been pampered since day one and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Spotless interior, flawless paint, and it drives like a cloud. You honestly won't find one better cared for than this. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
