    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine E92 M3, a definitive example of naturally aspirated engineering. This vehicle features the high-revving S65 V8 engine, delivering linear power up to an 8,400 RPM redline through eight individual throttle bodies. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal lateral kinematics and torque distribution. Meticulously maintained, the rod bearings and actuators have been serviced preventatively to ensure peak reciprocating assembly health. The carbon fiber roof remains structurally perfect with no clear-coat degradation, and the M-DCT dual-clutch transmission provides lightning-fast gear synchronization. This is a collector-grade specimen with zero thermal cycling fatigue on engine plastics and a completely stock, untouched exhaust manifold architecture.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
